title: American horror story asylum -  welcome to Briarcliff
author: ONCEUPON a HORRORSTORY
comment: Asylum is by far the best season, in my personal opinion.
It’s so sad to think that Pepper was always introduced as a baby killer. Imagine being unable to defend yourself and wanting to make a friend only to be cast as a horrible person.
I love this introduction of Lana. Her high heal crushing the cigarette, the fixing of her hair, the Carrie theme. Awesome
Sister Jude was def my favourite of Jessica Langes AHS roles.
description:
American horror story asylum - Lana winters visits the asylum 
2x1 welcome to Briarcliff
